title: Strangers in Paradise, Volume 11: Brave New World
description: This new trade paperback is the eleventh in the series! Katchoo is in Hawaii missing Francine, Francine is in Tennessee missing Katchoo. In two storylines that weave together, both girls make radical changes in their lives that bring them back together at last--but at what cost? A riveting storyline about love and friendship featuring two of the comic industry's most unlikely heroes.
author: Terry Moore
